{
  "note": "RomDrop feature patches (E85/flex-fuel, Speed Density, Alpha-N, extra spark/fuel tables). Apply with the official romdrop.exe (menu 'P | Patch Stock ROM') to a STOCK read, which generates a patched calibration; load THAT in the editor to edit the unlocked tables. Patch application is done by romdrop.exe (closed, checksum-verified via romdrop.crc) - NOT reimplemented here, to avoid corrupting an ECU. Note: patches add the CODE; the flex table VALUES start empty (0xFF) and are filled by the tuner.",
